No information.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF936A2CFA53925A1719BF41" pageId="104" pageNumber="862" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF936A2CFA53925A1719BF41" blockId="104.[1452,2660,279,1183]" pageId="104" pageNumber="862">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFF936A2CFA53925A190ABF16" bold="true" box="[1455,1802,1027,1060]" pageId="104" pageNumber="862">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Not assessed on The IUCN Red List. The species has a fairly restricted range across 
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFF936A2CF93392721926BF7E" box="[1743,1830,1067,1100]" name="Japan" pageId="104" pageNumber="862">Japan</collectingCountry>
, and seems to be relatively rare. Virtually nothing is known of its ecology and threats; further research is certainly needed.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
